the money goes to china if we spend it on gasoline it goes to the arabs if we buy a computer it will go to india if we purchase fruit and vegetables it will go to mexico honduras and guatemala if we purchase a good car it will go to germany if we purchase useless crap it will go to taiwan and none of it will help the american economy the only way to keep that money here at home is to spend it on prostitutes and beer since these are the only products still produced in us ive been doing my part booksedit tomorrows gold asias age of discovery  riding the millennial storm marc fabers path to profit in the financial markets with mani kiran  the great money illusion the confusion of the confusions  referencesedit  a b c faber marc in whos who of the asian pacific rim volume  pg  published by barons whos who    archived october   at the wayback machine  jessica pressler and bess levin  the fearmongers of finance retrieved    asia frontier capital ltd is a fund management company managing equities in asian frontier countries bangladesh cambodia iraq laos mongolia myanmar pakistan papua new guinea sri lanka vietnam  shareholders asiafrontiercapitalcom retrieved     archived october   at the wayback machine  sterngold james  hong kong empires junk tactic the new york times retrieved     archived september   at the wayback machine  sayson ian c and pimm fox  global markets face severe correction faber says bloomberg archived from the original on  retrieved  cs maint bot originalurl status unknown link  mctague jim  barrons cover dont bet the farm – part ii barrons dow jones retrieved    video  bloomberg business bloombergcom retrieved    mishs global economic trend analysis marc faber  bullish on the us bearish on commodities globaleconomicanalysisblogspotcom  retrieved    marc faber predicts economic disaster in  part  of  youtubecom retrieved    httpwwwmultplcomsphistoricalpricestablebyyear  us inflation to approach zimbabwe level faber says bloombergcom retrieved    httpwww